## Key Features

- Parallel processing (configurable workers)
- Multiple input formats (CSV, JSON, text, stdin)
- Multiple output formats (text, JSON, Markdown, HTML)
- Progress tracking with rich progress bars
- Error handling (continue-on-error mode)
- Detailed logging
- Aggregate analysis and reporting
- Critical alerting

## Usage

All utilities follow consistent patterns:
- Input from file, stdin, or direct arguments
- Parallel processing with --parallel
- Progress bars with --progress
- Output redirection with --output
- Format selection with --format

## Dependencies

- Python 3.7+
- google-cloud-bigquery (for dataset operations)
- rich (optional, for progress bars)
- Underlying tools: bq-profile, bq-table-compare, bq-optimize

## Testing

All utilities tested with --help flag and verified executable permissions.

Ready for production use.
